By far the loooongest logo we've ever designed.
.
This year, we were invited to design the @d_and_ad Festival 2020 identity, including naming, strategy and festival communication campaign.
.
Featuring super extended customised variable font (Marfa) by @abcdinamo
.
The D&AD festival is a three-day immersion in the world’s best craft, creativity and culture for the global creative industries taking place at The Old Truman Brewery, London.
.
.

DEMO - Design in Motion Festival @demo.festival
A festival celebrating the finest motion from the finest studio’s, designers, upcoming talents and art academies from all around the world. Showcasing work for 24 hours on all 80 digital screens located in Amsterdam Central train station 7 November.

Festival founded and designed by @StudioDumbar X @exterionmedianl
